# Gemini Browser Agent Skills — Cline / Roo Code

> Auto-loaded by Cline/Roo Code into system prompt. Lightweight router — ~200 tokens.

## CRITICAL RULES (Memorize — No File Load)

1. NEVER run Browser Subagent > 10 steps without pausing
2. ALWAYS summarize browser results BEFORE deleting artifacts
3. ALWAYS delete `.webp` recordings after browser sessions
4. ALWAYS verify file reading: state `"Read X/Y files"` before proceeding
5. NEVER delete entire `~/.gemini/antigravity` directory

## ROUTING TABLE (On-Demand Loading)

| When | Load This File |
|---|---|
| Before browser launch | `skills/browser-preflight/SKILL.md` |
| After browser returns | `skills/browser-cleanup/SKILL.md` |
| Disk > 10GB or "clean" | `skills/browser-heavy-cleanup/SKILL.md` |
| Any browser task | `rules/rule-using-browser.md` |
| Before writing code | `rules/self-check.md` |

## SELF-CHECK (Before Every Action)

```
📋 Active Rules: [list top 3]
📂 Files Read: X/Y (Missing: [none | list])
```
If files missing → read them NOW.

## CONTEXT COMPRESSION (After Browser)

After cleanup: `🗜️ Browser context compressed. Key findings: [3-5 bullets]`

## ERROR RECOVERY

- `[AI_SYSTEM_HINT]` in terminal → follow immediately
- Browser fails → load `skills/browser-cleanup/SKILL.md` BEFORE retry
- >15 messages → re-read routing table
